---

## Risk & Mitigation

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|-----------|
| Incomplete VC migration | Medium | High | Grep for direct endpoint invocations (`app.services.<service>.<endpoint>`); code review checklist; keep injection helpers intact |
| Regression in checkout | Low | High | Manual flow verification each migration; optional Appium if re-enabled |
| Memory leaks from singletons | Low | High | Profile with Instruments; use `[weak self]` in closures |
| Auth header loss | Low | High | Verify `SessionHeaderProvider` auto-injected in managers |
| JSON decode failures | Medium | Medium | Manager-level defensive parsing + manual scenario checks |
| Circular dependencies | Low | Medium | Strict rule: managers don't import VCs |

